high_descs: Walk ahead and slightly right to the right side of the stove.
Pick up the coffee mug on the counter.
Turn around and walk to the fridge.
Place the mug in the fridge in front of the red apple. Close the door, wait a moment, and take the mug out.
Turn around and veer right to the coffee maker.
Place the coffee mug in the coffee maker.
anns.task_desc: Place a chilled mug in a coffee maker.

high_descs: Go to the forward and stand in front of the counter to the right of the stove.
Pick the mug up from the counter.
Turn around and stand in front of the fridge.
Put the mug in the fridge and shut the door and then open the door and take the mug out again.
Turn around and go to the right to face the coffee maker on the counter.
Put the mug under the coffee maker on the counter.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled mug under a coffee maker.

high_descs: Move over to the counter that is in front and to the right of you.
Pick up the mug from the counter, to the right of the oven.
Turn left, walk to the wall, then turn left and walk up to the fridge.
Chill the mug in the fridge before taking it out and closing the door.
Turn left, walk a few steps, turn left, walk up to the oven, then turn right to face the coffee maker.
Place the mug on the coffee maker.
anns.task_desc: Move a chilled coffee mug to the coffee maker.
